Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Kid先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,霧散了 飛機似乎可以起飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就走吧
