Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:11.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我甚至覺得醒悟得太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對不起
