Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:40.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來得跟很多人下跪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:41.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那要放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然要唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:44.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
