Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:53.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:54.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有表演嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:56.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海大人露出真容了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,人家又沒想隱瞞 網路上一搜就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼情況 好厲害 好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:17.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好久沒聽到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,早期的AZALEA 這倒是常規形式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:26.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(就像為新球鞋穿上鞋帶一樣)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:31.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(懷著期待迎來今天 積極度過每一天吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(那些距離遙遠的人 說的露骨的話)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,AZALEA真棒啊\N(那些距離遙遠的人 說的露骨的話)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯\N(那些距離遙遠的人 說的露骨的話)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:36.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(那些距離遙遠的人 說的露骨的話)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:42.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(只有你了解你自己 用不著放在心上)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:46.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(刷上塗層的心無論融化多少次)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:50.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(只要再次刷上就好)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:54.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(活出自己的本色吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(沒錯 Brandnew day)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:59.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(無論何時 都能打開新的大門)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:02.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(稍微靠過來一點)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:05.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(看那光芒吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(上吧 Brandnew way)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:10.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(那樣的明天 我只想讓你一個人看見)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(不要猶豫 試著邁出腳步)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:17.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(不是夢的夢就在前方)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:21.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,靠這種做法是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(沒錯 Brandnew day)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:31.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(無論何時 都能打開新的大門)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(稍微靠過來一點)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(看那光芒吧)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:38.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(上吧 Brandnew way)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:42.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(那樣的明天 我只想讓你一個人看見)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:45.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(不要猶豫 試著邁出腳步)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:50.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(不是夢的夢就在前方)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:06.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:09.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海大人 我這輩子跟定你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:20.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓能理解的人理解就心滿意足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣又會回到無人問津的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你以為靠這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:30.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,靠這樣就能將音樂堅持下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:36.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或許你看不上吧 但這才是AZALEA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:39.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們還是想堅持這種風格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱著天真的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:41.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可沒辦法在這一行活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唐澤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:46.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便如此 我們依然要堅持音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:52.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 打擾各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去叫保全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:58.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我姓諸葛 名亮 字孔明…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這人是我的軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,軍師？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓您見笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你就是幕後主使…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:09.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是來嘲笑敗者的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,豈敢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是想把借走的東西還給各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:24.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,新生AZALEA？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是剛才的影像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:28.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,立刻讓人刪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:31.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,影片的讚數
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:34.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是吧 超過10萬讚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,草船借箭之計
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:41.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明曾從魏軍手中搶走了10萬支箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:44.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是現在 我們的孔明…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:48.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,秘技 草船借箭反轉之計
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,返還10萬讚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把讚還回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:57.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們已經喪失了SUMMER SONIA的出場權
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:00.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,事到如今 這東西毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:03.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:08.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我聽說AZALEA在演出 立刻就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對 趕緊來109前面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHORRY'S 從今天起我就是AZALEA粉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,帥氣的AZALEA我也好喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:19.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,AZALEA一直都是AZALEA啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這就結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,返場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:22.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我都沒聽成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:25.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不放演唱會的音源嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:30.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這些讚不同於用錢買來的讚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:35.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,安可 安可 安可…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海的音樂 被大家接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:45.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這些讚來自純粹被她們的歌曲打動的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,派對咖孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們的EIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:59.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,通過了10萬讚企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:02.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天店裡請客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-今天的快閃演唱會真的好勁爆啊 -是你這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:15.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,EIKO唱得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但AZALEA最後那首歌也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:20.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽說演唱會的影片讚數特別誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:23.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是托吧 畢竟是KEY TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:27.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不是KEY TIME的唐澤先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你居然來了 真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:33.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,帥死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是來做了斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之要先來一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:37.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就換一種酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:40.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不喝敵人的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:43.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們這下就與KEY TIME為敵了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼會與你為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只不過 戰爭的勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:51.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只有打過才知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:55.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,像你這樣逞強 最後銷聲匿跡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可認識好幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:15:01.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,銷聲匿跡的人指的是曾經的你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你年輕時不跟大唱片公司合作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:08.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟同伴一起堅持玩音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而 某一天遭到一位成員背叛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:12.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:16.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,人們只需要講述勝者的故事就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:20.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以 你一心想捧紅她們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想讓她們成為勝者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為防她們重蹈自己的覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:28.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比任何人都相信她們才能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:31.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唐澤先生 就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:34.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別輕易把才能掛在嘴邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是生意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她們有才能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:44.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 卻懷才不遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:47.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,音樂總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:51.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,走錯一步就會導致寶石被埋沒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 今天的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓她們的音樂獲得了廣泛認可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今後就算沒我 她們也能在這一行活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:01.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最早叫六本木烏龍麵店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:05.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唐澤 這跟當初說好的不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:08.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你不是要讓我們在體育場開巡演嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼時候過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們會支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:14.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:18.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個軍師給我們發了消息 說是能看到有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是你以前的樂隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超級帥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唐澤先生 原來你以前很搖滾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:29.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(我是主謀)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:30.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唐澤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天我們擅自行動了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:41.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 我們還是喜歡這樣的AZALEA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且現場演奏爽得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:47.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也一樣 比起跳舞 還是打鼓更順手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:54.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可否讓AZALEA保持現在的形式 再次包裝我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先提醒你們一下 音樂是生意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:06.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的這個想法不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:07.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個 可以的話 還請溫和一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:18.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你給的壓力太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還有 別再讓我們穿那服裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:25.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一定會捧紅你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是 還請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(恭喜EIKO 獲得SUMMER SONIA出場資格 ！！)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:52.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我真的要參加SUMMER SONIA啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是孔明帶我走到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:18:00.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要成為你的軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:04.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,軍師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:15.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不是英子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:21.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你離開沒事嗎 派對才剛開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:23.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事 倒是你 在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想來外面透透氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就過來喝酒慶祝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:32.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,確實 舞池全是人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:36.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都是被你的歌聲迷住的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:38.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正式說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:41.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,恭喜你贏得SUMMER SONIA出場資格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:44.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又不是我一個人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是因為你做了很多工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就是來向你道謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,曾經的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:03.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了勝利 付出再多犧牲也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是會奪走眾多生命的計謀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:07.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(離間之計)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:09.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這次的戰鬥中\N(離間之計)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也準備好了更深的計謀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過沒有派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子的歌聲讓民眾的心凝聚在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這都是英子的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該道謝的是我
